<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
   (These excellent ``separate buy'' articles are from the current
(week beginning Jan. 2, 1999 _ Happy New Year!) Economist
magazine.)  
  
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
in Canada except to The Toronto Globe &AMP; Mail.)  
  
 (To publish these articles, they must be purchased from the New
York Times Syndicate in New York at 1-800-972-3550 or 212-499-3333,
or fax us at 212-499-3382.)  
  
 (PLEASE NOTE: Each of these articles has been transmitted into the
``k'' commentary news file.)  
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; COMMENTARY &LR;  &QC; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; ONLY POETS CAN NOW SAVE MANKIND FROM MILLENNIUM BUGS &LR;  &QL;
