<P>
   &UR; IT'S TIME CLINTON'S SLOW-DRIP TORTURE OF AMERICA ENDS &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Moved as BC-DAMAGE-CLINTON-US-ECONOMIST-NYTSF......950 words &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; EURO: A UNITED STATES OF EUROPE? &LR;  &QL;
