<P>
   COP-ARREST (Seattle) _ An off duty police officer is arrested
for vehicular homicide after a 3 a.m. accident. Police say he was
drunk, and speeding. Acknowledging that all Washington state and
local cops just completed training in the new DUI laws, cops at the
scene say, ``We didn't set a good example.''
</P>
